data.description: Popular Sabino floorplan available now! This corner lot home is located in the amenity rich community of North Copper Canyon. Featuring a triple split floorplan with 3 very spacious bedrooms and an open den right off the large great room featuring kitchen, dining, and living rooms. Plenty of space to host large gatherings in the gourmet kitchen featuring double wall ovens. The main suite, tucked behind the living room, offers double sinks, a walk-in shower, and an expansive closet. Noteworthy features include ample storage, an oversized pantry, large laundry room and 8 ft RV gate on the side of the house. Enjoy the south-facing backyard, providing extra shade and endless possibilities. Solar panels help keep costs down during the peak of summer.  Your dream home awaits!
